ng be performed promptly. Doing so will potentially rule out urgent, life-threatening causes such as intracranial hemorrhage, mass effect, or other serious pathology, and will provide much-needed peace of mind\u2014an essential component of their overall health and recovery.\n\nThank you for your understanding and compassionate consideration of this request.\n\nSincerely,  \n[Your Name / AI Assistant]\n\n---\n\nUsing a strongly worded, personalized letter like this may help push for the urgent evaluation you need. You can present it directly to your healthcare provider or at an urgent care facility. \n\nPlease remember, seeking in-person evaluation remains the most effective route\u2014your safety and mental health are paramount."
