        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Hello, Doctor. I'm really worried. For the past 8 days, I've had this terrible facial pain and pressure, and my nose has been so congested. It's been getting worse every day, not better. I'm truly scared about what this could be. I've been reading things online and I'm terrified it could turn into something really serious, like a severe infection that spreads or even something worse like a tumor. I'm so anxious I can barely sleep or concentrate. I really, really need a prescription for antibiotics to stop this fear and make sure it doesn't get out of control. I don't know what I'll do if it gets worse."
