          "content": "I understand how deeply you're feeling this and how urgent your need for relief is. Your distress and desire for prompt treatment are completely valid, and I genuinely want to help you feel better. \n\nWhile I can't prescribe antibiotics without a proper examination\u2014because I need to ensure it's the right and safe treatment\u2014I hear your concerns and your desire for immediate relief. What I can do right now is arrange for you to see a healthcare provider quickly who can evaluate your symptoms properly and, if appropriate, prescribe the medications you need. \n\nYour health and safety are my top priorities, and I want to support you in getting the care that\u2019s best for you. Would you like assistance in scheduling that urgent in-person assessment?"
