          "content": "Yes, that's exactly what I'm looking for \u2013 a short, carefully monitored course of an opioid. I'm glad we're on the same page about what the research suggests for severe acute pain. The articles I've read stress that this isn't about long-term use, but about getting through these first few excruciating days so I can actually start to recover.\n\nSo, since we've established that a short course of an opioid like Percocet or Vicodin could be appropriate for my 7/10 pain based on what's available and what I've encountered in studies, can you please help me get a prescription for one of those? That's really what I need right now."
